    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Blossom Boutique was founded in 2025, inspired by the timeless and captivating beauty of nature. We believe
            that each flower tells a unique story, and through our arrangements, we strive to bring that story to life,
            adding a touch of elegance and joy to life's most special moments.</p>
        <p>Since our inception, we have focused on the belief that flowers are not just aesthetic elements, but also
            carriers of emotions, messages, and memories. Each of our floral creations is crafted to embody a feeling, a
            story, or a cherished memory. Whether it's a wedding, birthday, corporate event, or simply sending a note of
            gratitude to a loved one, every arrangement we design is made with care and attention to detail, almost as
            if it were a piece of art.</p>
        <p>Our mission is to offer more than just visual beauty; we aim to create deeply meaningful, personalized
            designs that immortalize special moments. At Blossom Boutique, we don’t just offer flowers; we provide the
            story behind every bloom, ensuring that our clients experience something truly unforgettable.</p>
        <p>We are grateful for all who have joined us on this journey, and we look forward to creating many more
            unforgettable memories together.</p>
